snippet: Suicide bombers in an explosives-laden car killed two soldiers in the volatile South Waziristan tribal region, according to a senior security official in Peshawar.
abstract: Suicide bombers in explosives-laden car strike Pakistani military base in South Waziristan tribal region, killing three soldiers.
lead_paragraph: Suicide bombers in an explosives-laden car killed two soldiers in the volatile South Waziristan tribal region, according to a senior security official in Peshawar.

headline.main: Bomb Attack Kills 3 at Base In Pakistan
